This file is for adding any lujvo or fu'ivla you create in the process
of translating the story.

-Robin

*	*	*

djataurte - 'tart', the food stuff. (orig use: chapter 11 title)

rutytisna - 'fruit-filled', 'tart' (rhymes with risna, as tarts does with hearts!)

manfyta'u 'livery, uniform' (ch. VI)

nargile 'hookah, nargileh' (ch. 4-5)

studukti 'antipodes' x1 is opposite x2 on sphere/circle x3 (ch. 1)
sludukti 'opposing muscle' x1 opposes muscle x2 in controlling x3 in body x4